This combination represents the premier 
\f1\b frontend design system stack for modern React development
\f0\b0 . It pairs a powerful UI framework with a high-performance styling engine and an accessible, copy-paste component architecture. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@sureshdotariya/shadcn-ui-tailwind-css-4-next-js-15-building-scalable-uis-in-2025-4de669b202fa"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/shadcn-ui-beginners-delwo-athauda-tjfyc"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}]\
