\f1\b highly customizable, lightning-fast, and fully accessible (WAI-ARIA compliance) user interfaces
\f0\b0  without fighting the boundaries of a rigid component library. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/shadcn-ui-beginners-delwo-athauda-tjfyc"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}]\
