{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://react.dev/blog/2024/12/05/react-19"}}{\fldrslt 
\f0\b0 \cf3 \ul \ulc3 React 19}}
\f0\b0  provides the core rendering engine and state management capabilities. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://react.dev/blog/2024/12/05/react-19"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v07gXY6ESEo&t=119"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.kellton.com/kellton-tech-blog/react-19-latest-features-and-updates"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://bitskingdom.com/blog/top-frontend-tools-2025/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 4}}]\
