\f1\b\fs32 \cf0 2. Tailwind CSS v4 (The Styling Engine) [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ud913ekwAOQ&t=135"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}]\
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4"}}{\fldrslt 
\f0\b0 \cf3 \ul \ulc3 Tailwind CSS v4}}
\f0\b0  serves as the utility-first CSS processor, completely rewritten in Rust for maximum speed. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://fireup.pro/news/tailwind-css-v4-0-released-lightning-fast-builds-advanced-features-and-simplified-setup"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.sitepoint.com/tailwind-css-in-react-and-nextjs/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://eagerworks.com/blog/tailwind-css-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 4}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@shahzaibnawaz/next-js-16-roadmap-day-4-30-styling-tailwind-css-4-css-modules-fonts-8aa725391fb8"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 5}}]\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Key Strengths
\f0\b0 : Powered by the high-performance 
\f1\b Lightning CSS
\f0\b0  engine, full builds execute up to 5x faster. It moves configuration out of JavaScript and into native CSS using the 
\f2\fs28 @theme
\f0\fs32  directive. It also features out-of-the-box container queries, automatic content detection (no more configuring content arrays), and advanced 3D transforms and gradient APIs. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://fireup.pro/news/tailwind-css-v4-0-released-lightning-fast-builds-advanced-features-and-simplified-setup"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ud913ekwAOQ&t=135"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://believemy.com/en/r/whats-new-in-tailwind-css-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 4}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://laravel-news.com/tailwind-css-v4-is-now-released"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 5}}]\
