Key Strengths
\f0\b0 : It focuses purely on 
\f1\b behavior, logic, and perfect accessibility
\f0\b0  (keyboard navigation, focus traps, and screen-reader ARIA attributes). Because it has zero opinion on styling, developers have absolute freedom to wrap these behaviors in custom visual layers. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/shadcn-ui-beginners-delwo-athauda-tjfyc"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@the.sikandar.dev/introduction-to-shadcn-ui-build-beautiful-accessible-react-components-46dfa3474295"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}]\
