\f0\b0 : It utilizes a CLI to drop the source code of beautifully crafted components directly into your application directory. It seamlessly combines 
\f1\b Radix UI for logic
\f0\b0  and 
\f1\b Tailwind CSS for styles
\f0\b0 . Modern iterations feature full 
\f2\fs28 data-slot
