\f1\b\fs40 \cf0 Why Choose This Stack?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\fs32 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Total Code Ownership:
\f0\b0  Because 
\f2\fs28 shadcn/ui
\f0\fs32  gives you raw source files, your project is immune to breaking updates common with traditional component dependencies. If a design needs to change fundamentally, you just modify the local file. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://uniquedevs.com/en/blog/shadcn-ui-component-library-for-react/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@the.sikandar.dev/introduction-to-shadcn-ui-build-beautiful-accessible-react-components-46dfa3474295"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://adminlte.io/blog/react-ui-frameworks/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}]\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Uncompromising Accessibility:
\f0\b0  Re-building accessible menus or modals from scratch is incredibly difficult. Radix ensures compliance out-of-the-box. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/shadcn-ui-beginners-delwo-athauda-tjfyc"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://medium.com/@the.sikandar.dev/introduction-to-shadcn-ui-build-beautiful-accessible-react-components-46dfa3474295"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}]\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Performance:
\f0\b0  Tailwind v4 builds your style sheet at microsecond speeds using Rust, and React 19 keeps client-side rendering efficient. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/reactjs/react-19-new-features-and-updates/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.angularminds.com/blog/whats-new-in-react-v19"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 3}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.digitalapplied.com/blog/tailwind-css-v4-migration-new-features-guide"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 4}}]\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
